{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/book/2020/03/09/读完「你不知道的JS」第一版.html","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"宫不上叔"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"100c377f-24b9-5061-ab6c-114bf1dfe3e9","excerpt":"读完「你不知道的 JS」第一版  「你不知道的 JS」是getify的一本关于深究 JavaScript…","html":"<h1>读完「你不知道的 JS」第一版</h1>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/e1596/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 76.806640625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/cbe2e/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.webp 148w,\n/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/3084c/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.webp 295w,\n/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/5ca24/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.webp 590w,\n/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/dad35/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.webp 885w,\n/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/2baf0/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.webp 1180w,\n/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/8df42/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.webp 2048w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/a80bd/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.jpg 148w,\n/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/1c91a/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.jpg 295w,\n/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/1c72d/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.jpg 590w,\n/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/a8a14/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.jpg 885w,\n/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/fbd2c/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.jpg 1180w,\n/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/e1596/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.jpg 2048w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/3ea1928807d517884278377426c78008/1c72d/2020-03-09-you-dont-know-about-JS.jpg\"\n          alt=\"book cover\"\n          title=\"book cover\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">book cover</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>「你不知道的 JS」是<a href=\"https://github.com/getify\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">getify</a>的一本关于深究 JavaScript 的书，中文版分为三册，前一阵子发现作者正在更新第二版，读了几页真的不错，于是找来第一版读了下。</p>\n<p>第一版第一册就是深究词法、上下文，这些东西大部分书都提的比较少，说实话，虽然我已经了解了，但是总是忘。这本书第二版比第一版好太多了，有兴趣的可以去读一下。</p>\n<p>第二册，异步，关于 promise 和生成器，应该是现有的关于异步写的最详细的书了，不过我更感兴趣他能更深度讲解一下 observable，虽然这个还不是 JavaScript 的标准。</p>\n<p>第三册，ES6 相关，很有趣的是，真本书前半部分都是关于第一第二册的简述，所以如果你刚好上不了网只能买书的话，直接看这一本也差不多。</p>\n<p>后面我可能会读一下书中推荐的<a href=\"https://github.com/getify/Functional-Light-JS\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Functiional Light JS</a>，以及 2ality 写的<a href=\"https://exploringjs.com/deep-js/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Deep JavaScript: Theory and techniques</a>。</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"book"},"fields":{"slug":"/book/2020/03/09/读完「你不知道的JS」第一版.html","date":"March 09, 2020","title":"读完「你不知道的JS」第一版"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/book/2020/03/09/读完「你不知道的JS」第一版.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/03/06/使用Utterance添加基於GitHub-issue的評論系統.html","title":"使用Utterance添加基於GitHub-issue的評論系統"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/03/10/腾讯云docker安装strapi.html","title":"腾讯云docker安装strapi"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}}}}}